---
title: Coq au Vin Style Pie with Parsley Mash
description: We’ve transformed this classic French dish into a much loved British favourite: pie and mash! But do not be mistaken...this is no ordinary pie and mash! A deliciously rich and warming filling tucked in with golden pastry and served alongside buttery parsley mash makes this recipe a perfect midweek showstopper. It’s hard to think of a reason why you wouldn’t fall head over heels for this dish.
